Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此  我第二个愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就今天想与你一起去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把这地方当作只属于你我的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一起学习  一起吃饭  一起扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再与祐一君一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个愿望是否可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是约定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是我能办到的  什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起这里就是学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有严格的校规  也不需要穿规定的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,自由的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,考试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有考试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想休息的时候就休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想什么时候来就来  想什么时候走就走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伙食每天都会有鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都有鲷鱼烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对  每天鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,每天的话有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的  要每天都有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们再在这所学校见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  下次我来这个小镇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,见面的地方是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一言为定哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮了～　天亮了～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快点吃完早饭上学啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们无法再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,失去你的圆舞曲\N～ronde～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也起得很早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由没有回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,回到了自己家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不适的话请假也无妨哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说  在「多世界解释」中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,活着的猫和死了的猫是同时存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道通讯地址什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由的住址  电话什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道那家伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好吃饭可不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,早饭也剩下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一真的喜欢亚由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没  没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好迟啊　祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,找到亚由了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为在这等的话她就会来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我和她见面的地方总是在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也尝试问了下学校里的同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在森林里果然没有什么学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,找到亚由丢失的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看  都是些不可思议的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那森林的广场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由失落的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么忘记了7年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有书包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定会回来取的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是亚由中意的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  请来两份草莓冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,草莓冰激凌两份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吃好吃的东西会变得精神起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要加油哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由没有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不  还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要尽量给他鼓劲哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是一家人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,必须相互扶持着生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有可以成为线索的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,功课作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也用不着两个人一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以分工合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我也可以变得轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说到头是自己想偷懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那祐一要自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那我做哪部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你  自己说要做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,却怎么睡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,人家困嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！ 加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我们也这样做过寒假作业呢  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不记得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说一些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我不是都道歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你刚才踩了我的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没做哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  皮洛  皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,皮洛  皮洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪  要睡就去床上睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呜呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要呜呢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也不要扑哟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.75,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,形容胸部颤抖的象声词
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  为我打气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一君  好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕  我好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  不是有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,出了森林后  会有光亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是森林  是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要松开手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我在紧紧地握着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且算是森林外边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这个地方哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要出了森林  那便是囊中之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  祐一君你知道时空胶囊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,里面存放值得回忆的东西的那玩意是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个能不能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,往里面放什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,放这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,行是行  不过不是还留有一个愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经让你帮助实现2个了  已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的留给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,或是为了到时候送给谁去实现那人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过来实现愿望的不是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧  祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有标志  能不能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有需要这个娃娃的人的话  一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为了转往别的学校的祐一君而进行送别会哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拉钩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这样还不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很成问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这件睡衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的猫是草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这边角落里的猫是葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是黄瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,全都有名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  那个闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,台词能不能重新录下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  不可以哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,人家费了不少力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只有两句而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此人家也费了不少力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我对于机器不在行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,最后让妈妈帮忙来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子阿姨也真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来照顾名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  非常感谢她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是只有你们两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不过一点也不寂寞哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望亚由能早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是小雪兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雪兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁作的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  要迟到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是它好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一只眼睛不知道跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  可以用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直带在身上的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  祐一送给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不做好它便不会罢休不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大小有点不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这就需要它多担待些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一  看到雪兔后没有想起些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想起了为了生病的父母而作了雪兔的一个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个相识的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法去动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,便做了一大堆雪兔取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给她母亲看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个孩子的母亲如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲的病治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,和女孩过了幸福美满的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想起了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的埋在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由要找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那家伙挖这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓啦  反正很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会记着你的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,若能再找些人手的话倒是会更有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,又不能去拜托香里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一会不填上的话会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是被别人挖走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说这也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也有可能依然被埋在下边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要加油哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  是不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  让你干这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  我能做的也就这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,做好了  虽然还沾有泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  多谢  名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这会成为寻找亚由的线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今天让你陪了我很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  因为我也玩得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是换了发型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  小学的时候你没有梳三条小辫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  三条小辫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只梳了一年左右就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮了～　天亮了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃早饭了哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一  去上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是梦啊  快起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我被名雪唤醒  这样的事情不现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一说的好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天为什么起的这么早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也想试着叫醒祐一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能每天如此就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有些寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴  亚由都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈喜欢热闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一  不会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去的只有这个家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚上吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,草莓蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,又是草莓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是草莓蛋糕的话  我一日三餐都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕我也会买好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  快瞧  还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你们在磨蹭什么  要迟到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  快走祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  在你回去前能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我从早上就一直找你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  它叫雪兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是我做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我只能准备这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我手不巧  所以花了些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想送给祐一  所以拼命制作的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呐  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你能接受它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然明天起我们就要变得一段时间无法见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你还会再来见我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然一直没能开口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是喜欢祐一的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,水濑  相泽你也过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,水濑  你的母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的母亲遇到交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,据说被救护车送走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都因为我说想吃什么草莓蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈才…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.93,0:23:46.32,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙一直都记着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,出去  祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想见任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人静静…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
